rComments: Paulette is an absolute joy! You can tell she's passionate about her work and really wants to help her students. She wants everyone to succeed and is as good at listening as she is lecturing. Probably my favourite professor at Western - a truly lovely woman.

She was a very dynamic prof, more interested in her own project than in the teaching, but we were a huge class too. I have not learned a whole lot. Definitely hot! Something nice in that boring place.
